<p>Popular open-source Javascript syntax highlighter.
</p>
<p>
<a style="color: #235bab;" href="http://www.xqueryhacker.com">Rob Whitby</a> entered his venerable <a style="color: #235bab;" href="http://www.xqueryhacker.com/2009/11/syntaxhighlighter-xquery-brush/">XQuery brush</a> and has claimed this bounty.  It's working decently as it always has.  <a style="color: #235bab;" href="http://alexgorbatchev.com">Alex Gorbachev</a> has "put it in the queue" for integration. 
</p>
