<p> </p>
<p>Well, that's the details.  It's likely we'll run another bounty hunting contest in the coming months.  If you have thoughts on projects like this one that would benefit our community, give me a holler.  I'm off to go ship some iPads and a Safari subscription to the folks who helped us out here</p>
